### ğŸ” 2. Strategic Benefits of OSS for Builders

| Benefit | Description | Real-World Example |
|--------|-------------|--------------------|
| ğŸš€ Audience | People discover your work by searching GitHub, not Google | Your README = SEO magnet  
| ğŸ”— Reputation | Contributions become your **proof of work** | Recruiters / collaborators find you  
| ğŸ§  Feedback | Issues and PRs become product insights | Users tell you where your logic breaks  
| ğŸ§° Infrastructure | Others build on your system â†’ adds value without your time | Plugins, forks, wrappers  
| ğŸ’¸ Indirect Revenue | Sell support, training, private forks | The product is free â€” the **relationship** is not  

> "Open source isn't the opposite of monetization. It's the front door."

